Package request_result.result

Class RegisterResult

java.lang.Object
request_result.result.Result
request_result.result.LoginResult
request_result.result.RegisterResult
public class RegisterResult
extends LoginResult
This class represents the register result message of the register service. It utilizes the functionality of the login result class since the response bodies contain the same data.
